Release 4.0.1-rc5
-----------------

Build Date : 2015-07-30
Locale     : GB
Checksum   : 
Size       : Size: 4.25 MB (7.69 MB available)

[New Features]

[Improvements]
* Antenna scan completes and selects best antenna

